text: The Fly V Australia () was an Australian road cycling team. The team was sponsored by Australia airline V Australia, and competed on the UCI Continental Tour. Riders on the team included Jonathan Cantwell, Bernard Sulzberger, Henk Vogels, David Kemp and David Tanner. The team found some success in the USA. ==References== Category:Cycling teams based in Australia Category:UCI Continental Teams (Oceania) Category:Cycling teams established in 2009 Category:Cycling teams disestablished in 2011
